var book = {
	"name": "Revelation",
	"numChapters": 22,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The Revelation of Jesus Christ, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30700A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30700A\"></sup>God gave Him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30700B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30700B\"></sup>show to His bond-servants, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30700C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30700C\"></sup>the things which must soon take place; and He sent and communicated <i>it</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30700D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30700D\"></sup>by His angel to His bond-servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30700E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30700E\"></sup>John,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>who testified to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30701F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30701F\"></sup>the word of God and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30701G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30701G\"></sup>the testimony of Jesus Christ, <i>even</i> to all that he saw.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30702H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30702H\"></sup>Blessed is he who reads and those who hear the words of the prophecy, and heed the things which are written in it; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30702I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30702I\"></sup>for the time is near.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30703J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30703J\"></sup>John to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30703K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30703K\"></sup>the seven churches that are in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30703L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30703L\"></sup>Asia: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30703M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30703M\"></sup>Grace to you and peace, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30703N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30703N\"></sup>Him who is and who was and who is to come, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30703O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30703O\"></sup>the seven Spirits who are before His throne,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and from Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30704P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30704P\"></sup>the faithful witness, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30704Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30704Q\"></sup>firstborn of the dead, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30704R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30704R\"></sup>ruler of the kings of the earth. To Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30704S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30704S\"></sup>loves us and released us from our sins by His blood—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and He has made us <i>to be</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30705T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30705T\"></sup>kingdom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30705U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30705U\"></sup>priests to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30705V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30705V\"></sup>His God and Father—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30705W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30705W\"></sup>to Him <i>be</i> the glory and the dominion forever and ever. Amen.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30706X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30706X\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold, He is coming with the clouds</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30706Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30706Y\"></sup>every eye will see Him, even those who pierced Him; and all the tribes of the earth will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30706Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30706Z\"></sup>mourn over Him. So it is to be. Amen.",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30707AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30707AA\"></sup>the Alpha and the Omega,”</span> says the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30707AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30707AB\"></sup>Lord God, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30707AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30707AC\"></sup>who is and who was and who is to come, the Almighty.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30708AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30708AD\"></sup>I, John, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30708AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30708AE\"></sup>brother and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30708AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30708AF\"></sup>fellow partaker in the tribulation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30708AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30708AG\"></sup>kingdom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30708AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30708AH\"></sup>perseverance <i>which are</i> in Jesus, was on the island called Patmos <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30708AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30708AI\"></sup>because of the word of God and the testimony of Jesus.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30709AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30709AJ\"></sup>in the Spirit on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30709AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30709AK\"></sup>the Lord’s day, and I heard behind me a loud voice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30709AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30709AL\"></sup>like <i>the sound</i> of a trumpet,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AM\"></sup>Write in a book what you see, and send <i>it</i> to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AN\"></sup>seven churches: to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AO\"></sup>Ephesus and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AP\"></sup>Smyrna and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AQ\"></sup>Pergamum and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AR\"></sup>Thyatira and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AS\"></sup>Sardis and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AT\"></sup>Philadelphia and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30710AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30710AU\"></sup>Laodicea.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then I turned to see the voice that was speaking with me. And having turned I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30711AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30711AV\"></sup>seven golden lampstands;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30712AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30712AW\"></sup>in the middle of the lampstands <i>I saw</i> one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30712AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30712AX\"></sup>like a son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30712AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30712AY\"></sup>clothed in a robe reaching to the feet, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30712AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30712AZ\"></sup>girded across His chest with a golden sash.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>His head and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30713BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30713BA\"></sup>hair were white like white wool, like snow; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30713BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30713BB\"></sup>His eyes were like a flame of fire.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30714BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30714BC\"></sup>feet <i>were</i> like burnished bronze, when it has been made to glow in a furnace, and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30714BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30714BD\"></sup>voice <i>was</i> like the sound of many waters.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In His right hand He held <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30715BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30715BE\"></sup>seven stars, and out of His mouth came a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30715BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30715BF\"></sup>sharp two-edged sword; and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30715BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30715BG\"></sup>face was like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30715BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30715BH\"></sup>the sun shining in its strength.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>When I saw Him, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30716BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30716BI\"></sup>fell at His feet like a dead man. And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30716BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30716BJ\"></sup>placed His right hand on me, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30716BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30716BK\"></sup>Do not be afraid; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30716BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30716BL\"></sup>I am the first and the last,</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30717BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30717BM\"></sup>living One; and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30717BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30717BN\"></sup>was dead, and behold, I am alive forevermore, and I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30717BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30717BO\"></sup>the keys of death and of Hades.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30718BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30718BP\"></sup>write <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30718BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30718BQ\"></sup>the things which you have seen, and the things which are, and the things which will take place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30718BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30718BR\"></sup>after these things.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30719BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30719BS\"></sup>mystery of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30719BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30719BT\"></sup>seven stars which you saw in My right hand, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30719BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30719BU\"></sup>seven golden lampstands: the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30719BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30719BV\"></sup>seven stars are the angels of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30719BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30719BW\"></sup>the seven churches, and the seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30719BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30719BX\"></sup>lampstands are the seven churches.</span>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>“To the angel of the church in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30720A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30720A\"></sup>Ephesus write:</span><span class=\"woj\">The One who holds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30720B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30720B\"></sup>the seven stars in His right hand, the One who walks <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30720C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30720C\"></sup>among the seven golden lampstands, says this:</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30721D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30721D\"></sup>I know your deeds and your toil and perseverance, and that you cannot tolerate evil men, and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30721E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30721E\"></sup>put to the test those who call themselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30721F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30721F\"></sup>apostles, and they are not, and you found them <i>to be</i> false;</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and you have perseverance and have endured <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30722G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30722G\"></sup>for My name’s sake, and have not grown weary.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But I have <i>this</i> against you, that you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30723H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30723H\"></sup>left your first love.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore remember from where you have fallen, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30724I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30724I\"></sup>repent and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30724J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30724J\"></sup>do the deeds you did at first; or else I am coming to you and will remove your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30724K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30724K\"></sup>lampstand out of its place—unless you repent.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Yet this you do have, that you hate the deeds of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30725L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30725L\"></sup>Nicolaitans, which I also hate.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30726M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30726M\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30726N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30726N\"></sup>To him who overcomes, I will grant to eat of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30726O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30726O\"></sup>the tree of life which is in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30726P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30726P\"></sup>Paradise of God.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30727Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30727Q\"></sup>Smyrna write:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30727R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30727R\"></sup>The first and the last, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30727S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30727S\"></sup>was dead, and has come to life, says this:</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘I know your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30728T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30728T\"></sup>tribulation and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30728U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30728U\"></sup>poverty (but you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30728V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30728V\"></sup>rich), and the blasphemy by those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30728W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30728W\"></sup>say they are Jews and are not, but are a synagogue of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30728X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30728X\"></sup>Satan.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not fear what you are about to suffer. Behold, the devil is about to cast some of you into prison, so that you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30729Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30729Y\"></sup>tested, and you will have tribulation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30729Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30729Z\"></sup>for ten days. Be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30729AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30729AA\"></sup>faithful until death, and I will give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30729AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30729AB\"></sup>the crown of life.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30730AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30730AC\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30730AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30730AD\"></sup>He who overcomes will not be hurt by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30730AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30730AE\"></sup>second death.’</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30731AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30731AF\"></sup>Pergamum write:</span><span class=\"woj\">The One who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30731AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30731AG\"></sup>the sharp two-edged sword says this:</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘I know where you dwell, where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30732AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30732AH\"></sup>Satan’s throne is; and you hold fast My name, and did not deny <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30732AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30732AI\"></sup>My faith even in the days of Antipas, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30732AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30732AJ\"></sup>witness, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30732AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30732AK\"></sup>faithful one, who was killed among you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30732AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30732AL\"></sup>where Satan dwells.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30733AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30733AM\"></sup>I have a few things against you, because you have there some who hold the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30733AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30733AN\"></sup>teaching of Balaam, who kept teaching Balak to put a stumbling block before the sons of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30733AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30733AO\"></sup>to eat things sacrificed to idols and to commit <i>acts of</i> immorality.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So you also have some who in the same way hold the teaching of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30734AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30734AP\"></sup>Nicolaitans.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30735AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30735AQ\"></sup>repent; or else <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30735AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30735AR\"></sup>I am coming to you quickly, and I will make war against them with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30735AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30735AS\"></sup>the sword of My mouth.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30736AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30736AT\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30736AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30736AU\"></sup>To him who overcomes, to him I will give <i>some</i> of the hidden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30736AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30736AV\"></sup>manna, and I will give him a white stone, and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30736AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30736AW\"></sup>new name written on the stone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30736AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30736AX\"></sup>which no one knows but he who receives it.’</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30737AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30737AY\"></sup>Thyatira write:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30737AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30737AZ\"></sup>The Son of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30737BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30737BA\"></sup>who has eyes like a flame of fire, and His feet are like burnished bronze, says this:</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30738BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30738BB\"></sup>I know your deeds, and your love and faith and service and perseverance, and that your deeds of late are greater than at first.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30739BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30739BC\"></sup>I have <i>this</i> against you, that you tolerate the woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30739BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30739BD\"></sup>Jezebel, who calls herself a prophetess, and she teaches and leads My bond-servants astray so that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30739BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30739BE\"></sup>commit <i>acts of</i> immorality and eat things sacrificed to idols.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30740BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30740BF\"></sup>I gave her time to repent, and she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30740BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30740BG\"></sup>does not want to repent of her immorality.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Behold, I will throw her on a bed <i>of sickness</i>, and those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30741BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30741BH\"></sup>commit adultery with her into great tribulation, unless they repent of her deeds.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And I will kill her children with pestilence, and all the churches will know that I am He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30742BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30742BI\"></sup>searches the minds and hearts; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30742BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30742BJ\"></sup>I will give to each one of you according to your deeds.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But I say to you, the rest who are in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30743BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30743BK\"></sup>Thyatira, who do not hold this teaching, who have not known the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30743BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30743BL\"></sup>deep things of Satan, as they call them—I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30743BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30743BM\"></sup>place no other burden on you.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Nevertheless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30744BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30744BN\"></sup>what you have, hold fast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30744BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30744BO\"></sup>until I come.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30745BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30745BP\"></sup>He who overcomes, and he who keeps My deeds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30745BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30745BQ\"></sup>until the end, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30745BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30745BR\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">to him I will give authority over the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">nations</span>;</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">and he shall</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30746BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30746BS\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">rule them with a rod of iron</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30746BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30746BT\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">as the vessels of the potter are broken to pieces,</span> as I also have received <i>authority</i> from My Father;</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>and I will give him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30747BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30747BU\"></sup>the morning star.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30748BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30748BV\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.’</span>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>“To the angel of the church in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30749A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30749A\"></sup>Sardis write:</span><span class=\"woj\">He who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30749B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30749B\"></sup>the seven Spirits of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30749C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30749C\"></sup>the seven stars, says this: ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30749D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30749D\"></sup>I know your deeds, that you have a name that you are alive, but you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30749E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30749E\"></sup>dead.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Wake up, and strengthen the things that remain, which were about to die; for I have not found your deeds completed in the sight of My God.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30751F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30751F\"></sup>remember what you have received and heard; and keep <i>it</i>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30751G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30751G\"></sup>repent. Therefore if you do not wake up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30751H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30751H\"></sup>I will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30751I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30751I\"></sup>like a thief, and you will not know at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30751J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30751J\"></sup>what hour I will come to you.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But you have a few <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30752K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30752K\"></sup>people in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30752L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30752L\"></sup>Sardis who have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30752M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30752M\"></sup>soiled their garments; and they will walk with Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30752N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30752N\"></sup>in white, for they are worthy.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30753O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30753O\"></sup>He who overcomes will thus be clothed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30753P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30753P\"></sup>white garments; and I will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30753Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30753Q\"></sup>erase his name from the book of life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30753R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30753R\"></sup>I will confess his name before My Father and before His angels.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30754S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30754S\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30755T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30755T\"></sup>Philadelphia write:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30755U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30755U\"></sup>He who is holy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30755V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30755V\"></sup>who is true, who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30755W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30755W\"></sup>the key of David, who opens and no one will shut, and who shuts and no one opens, says this:</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30756X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30756X\"></sup>I know your deeds. Behold, I have put before you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30756Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30756Y\"></sup>an open door which no one can shut, because you have a little power, and have kept My word, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30756Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30756Z\"></sup>have not denied My name.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Behold, I will cause <i>those</i> of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30757AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30757AA\"></sup>the synagogue of Satan, who say that they are Jews and are not, but lie—I will make them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30757AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30757AB\"></sup>come and bow down at your feet, and <i>make them</i> know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30757AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30757AC\"></sup>I have loved you.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30758AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30758AD\"></sup>kept the word of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30758AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30758AE\"></sup>My perseverance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30758AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30758AF\"></sup>I also will keep you from the hour of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30758AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30758AG\"></sup>testing, that <i>hour</i> which is about to come upon the whole <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30758AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30758AH\"></sup>world, to test <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30758AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30758AI\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30759AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30759AJ\"></sup>I am coming quickly; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30759AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30759AK\"></sup>hold fast what you have, so that no one will take your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30759AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30759AL\"></sup>crown.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30760AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30760AM\"></sup>He who overcomes, I will make him a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30760AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30760AN\"></sup>pillar in the temple of My God, and he will not go out from it anymore; and I will write on him the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30760AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30760AO\"></sup>name of My God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30760AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30760AP\"></sup>the name of the city of My God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30760AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30760AQ\"></sup>the new Jerusalem, which comes down out of heaven from My God, and My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30760AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30760AR\"></sup>new name.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30761AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30761AS\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.’</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“To the angel of the church in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30762AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30762AT\"></sup>Laodicea write:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30762AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30762AU\"></sup>The Amen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30762AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30762AV\"></sup>the faithful and true Witness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30762AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30762AW\"></sup>the Beginning of the creation of God, says this:</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30763AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30763AX\"></sup>I know your deeds, that you are neither cold nor hot; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30763AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30763AY\"></sup>I wish that you were cold or hot.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So because you are lukewarm, and neither hot nor cold, I will spit you out of My mouth.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Because you say, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30765AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30765AZ\"></sup>I am rich, and have become wealthy, and have need of nothing,” and you do not know that you are wretched and miserable and poor and blind and naked,</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I advise you to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30766BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30766BA\"></sup>buy from Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30766BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30766BB\"></sup>gold refined by fire so that you may become rich, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30766BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30766BC\"></sup>white garments so that you may clothe yourself, and <i>that</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30766BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30766BD\"></sup>the shame of your nakedness will not be revealed; and eye salve to anoint your eyes so that you may see.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30767BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30767BE\"></sup>Those whom I love, I reprove and discipline; therefore be zealous and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30767BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30767BF\"></sup>repent.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Behold, I stand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30768BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30768BG\"></sup>at the door and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30768BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30768BH\"></sup>knock; if anyone hears My voice and opens the door, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30768BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30768BI\"></sup>I will come in to him and will dine with him, and he with Me.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30769BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30769BJ\"></sup>He who overcomes, I will grant to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30769BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30769BK\"></sup>to sit down with Me on My throne, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30769BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30769BL\"></sup>I also overcame and sat down with My Father on His throne.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30770BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30770BM\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.’”</span>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30771A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30771A\"></sup>these things I looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30771B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30771B\"></sup>a door <i>standing</i> open in heaven, and the first voice which I had heard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30771C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30771C\"></sup>like <i>the sound</i> of a trumpet speaking with me, said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30771D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30771D\"></sup>Come up here, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30771E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30771E\"></sup>show you what must take place after these things.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Immediately I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30772F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30772F\"></sup>in the Spirit; and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30772G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30772G\"></sup>a throne was standing in heaven, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30772H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30772H\"></sup>One sitting on the throne.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And He who was sitting <i>was</i> like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30773I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30773I\"></sup>jasper stone and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30773J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30773J\"></sup>sardius in appearance; and <i>there was</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30773K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30773K\"></sup>rainbow around the throne, like an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30773L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30773L\"></sup>emerald in appearance.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30774M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30774M\"></sup>Around the throne <i>were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30774N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30774N\"></sup>twenty-four thrones; and upon the thrones <i>I saw</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30774O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30774O\"></sup>twenty-four elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30774P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30774P\"></sup>sitting, clothed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30774Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30774Q\"></sup>white garments, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30774R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30774R\"></sup>golden crowns on their heads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Out from the throne come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30775S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30775S\"></sup>flashes of lightning and sounds and peals of thunder. And <i>there were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30775T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30775T\"></sup>seven lamps of fire burning before the throne, which are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30775U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30775U\"></sup>the seven Spirits of God;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and before the throne <i>there was something</i> like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30776V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30776V\"></sup>sea of glass, like crystal; and in the center and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30776W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30776W\"></sup>around the throne, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30776X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30776X\"></sup>four living creatures <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30776Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30776Y\"></sup>full of eyes in front and behind.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30777Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30777Z\"></sup>The first creature <i>was</i> like a lion, and the second creature like a calf, and the third creature had a face like that of a man, and the fourth creature <i>was</i> like a flying eagle.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30778AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30778AA\"></sup>four living creatures, each one of them having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30778AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30778AB\"></sup>six wings, are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30778AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30778AC\"></sup>full of eyes around and within; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30778AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30778AD\"></sup>day and night they do not cease to say,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30778AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30778AE\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Holy, holy, holy</span> <i>is</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30778AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30778AF\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord God, the Almighty</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30778AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30778AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">who was and who is and who</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">is to come</span>.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when the living creatures give glory and honor and thanks to Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30779AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30779AH\"></sup>sits on the throne, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30779AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30779AI\"></sup>Him who lives forever and ever,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30780AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30780AJ\"></sup>twenty-four elders will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30780AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30780AK\"></sup>fall down before Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30780AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30780AL\"></sup>sits on the throne, and will worship <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30780AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30780AM\"></sup>Him who lives forever and ever, and will cast their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30780AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30780AN\"></sup>crowns before the throne, saying,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30781AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30781AO\"></sup>Worthy are You, our Lord and our God, to receive glory and honor and power; for You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30781AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30781AP\"></sup>created all things, and because of Your will they existed, and were created.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>I saw in the right hand of Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30782A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30782A\"></sup>sat on the throne a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30782B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30782B\"></sup>book written inside and on the back, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30782C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30782C\"></sup>sealed up with seven seals.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30783D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30783D\"></sup>strong angel proclaiming with a loud voice, “Who is worthy to open the book and to break its seals?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30784E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30784E\"></sup>in heaven or on the earth or under the earth was able to open the book or to look into it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I <i>began</i> to weep greatly because no one was found worthy to open the book or to look into it;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and one of the elders *said to me, “Stop weeping; behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30786F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30786F\"></sup>Lion that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30786G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30786G\"></sup>from the tribe of Judah, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30786H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30786H\"></sup>Root of David, has overcome so as to open the book and its seven seals.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I saw between the throne (with the four living creatures) and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30787I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30787I\"></sup>the elders a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30787J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30787J\"></sup>Lamb standing, as if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30787K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30787K\"></sup>slain, having seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30787L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30787L\"></sup>horns and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30787M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30787M\"></sup>seven eyes, which are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30787N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30787N\"></sup>the seven Spirits of God, sent out into all the earth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And He came and took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30788O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30788O\"></sup>the book out of the right hand of Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30788P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30788P\"></sup>sat on the throne.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When He had taken the book, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30789Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30789Q\"></sup>four living creatures and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30789R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30789R\"></sup>twenty-four elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30789S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30789S\"></sup>fell down before the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30789T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30789T\"></sup>Lamb, each one holding a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30789U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30789U\"></sup>harp and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30789V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30789V\"></sup>golden bowls full of incense, which are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30789W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30789W\"></sup>prayers of the saints.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And they *sang a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30790X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30790X\"></sup>new song, saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30790Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30790Y\"></sup>Worthy are You to take the book and to break its seals; for You were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30790Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30790Z\"></sup>slain, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30790AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30790AA\"></sup>purchased for God with Your blood <i>men</i> from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30790AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30790AB\"></sup>every tribe and tongue and people and nation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“You have made them <i>to be</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30791AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30791AC\"></sup>kingdom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30791AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30791AD\"></sup>priests to our God; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30791AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30791AE\"></sup>reign upon the earth.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I looked, and I heard the voice of many angels <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30792AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30792AF\"></sup>around the throne and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30792AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30792AG\"></sup>living creatures and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30792AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30792AH\"></sup>elders; and the number of them was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30792AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30792AI\"></sup>myriads of myriads, and thousands of thousands,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>saying with a loud voice,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30793AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30793AJ\"></sup>Worthy is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30793AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30793AK\"></sup>Lamb that was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30793AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30793AL\"></sup>slain to receive power and riches and wisdom and might and honor and glory and blessing.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30794AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30794AM\"></sup>every created thing which is in heaven and on the earth and under the earth and on the sea, and all things in them, I heard saying,“To Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30794AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30794AN\"></sup>sits on the throne, and to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30794AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30794AO\"></sup>Lamb, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30794AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30794AP\"></sup><i>be</i> blessing and honor and glory and dominion forever and ever.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30795AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30795AQ\"></sup>four living creatures kept saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30795AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30795AR\"></sup>Amen.” And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30795AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30795AS\"></sup>elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30795AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30795AT\"></sup>fell down and worshiped."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Then I saw when the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30796A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30796A\"></sup>Lamb broke one of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30796B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30796B\"></sup>seven seals, and I heard one of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30796C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30796C\"></sup>four living creatures saying as with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30796D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30796D\"></sup>voice of thunder, “Come.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I looked, and behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30797E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30797E\"></sup>white horse, and he who sat on it had a bow; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30797F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30797F\"></sup>a crown was given to him, and he went out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30797G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30797G\"></sup>conquering and to conquer.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When He broke the second seal, I heard the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30798H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30798H\"></sup>second living creature saying, “Come.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30799I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30799I\"></sup>a red horse, went out; and to him who sat on it, it was granted to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30799J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30799J\"></sup>take peace from the earth, and that <i>men</i> would slay one another; and a great sword was given to him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When He broke the third seal, I heard the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30800K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30800K\"></sup>third living creature saying, “Come.” I looked, and behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30800L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30800L\"></sup>black horse; and he who sat on it had a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30800M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30800M\"></sup>pair of scales in his hand.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I heard <i>something</i> like a voice in the center of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30801N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30801N\"></sup>four living creatures saying, “A quart of wheat for a denarius, and three quarts of barley for a denarius; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30801O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30801O\"></sup>do not damage the oil and the wine.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the Lamb broke the fourth seal, I heard the voice of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30802P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30802P\"></sup>fourth living creature saying, “Come.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I looked, and behold, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30803Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30803Q\"></sup>ashen horse; and he who sat on it had the name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30803R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30803R\"></sup>Death; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30803S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30803S\"></sup>Hades was following with him. Authority was given to them over a fourth of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30803T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30803T\"></sup>to kill with sword and with famine and with pestilence and by the wild beasts of the earth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When the Lamb broke the fifth seal, I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30804U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30804U\"></sup>underneath the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30804V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30804V\"></sup>altar the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30804W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30804W\"></sup>souls of those who had been slain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30804X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30804X\"></sup>because of the word of God, and because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30804Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30804Y\"></sup>testimony which they had maintained;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and they cried out with a loud voice, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30805Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30805Z\"></sup>How long, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30805AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30805AA\"></sup>Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30805AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30805AB\"></sup>holy and true, will You refrain from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30805AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30805AC\"></sup>judging and avenging our blood on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30805AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30805AD\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30806AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30806AE\"></sup>there was given to each of them a white robe; and they were told that they should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30806AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30806AF\"></sup>rest for a little while longer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30806AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30806AG\"></sup>until <i>the number of</i> their fellow servants and their brethren who were to be killed even as they had been, would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30806AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30806AH\"></sup>completed also.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I looked when He broke the sixth seal, and there was a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30807AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30807AI\"></sup>earthquake; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30807AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30807AJ\"></sup>sun became black as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30807AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30807AK\"></sup>sackcloth <i>made</i> of hair, and the whole moon became like blood;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30808AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30808AL\"></sup>the stars of the sky fell to the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30808AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30808AM\"></sup>as a fig tree casts its unripe figs when shaken by a great wind.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30809AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30809AN\"></sup>The sky was split apart like a scroll when it is rolled up, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30809AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30809AO\"></sup>every mountain and island were moved out of their places.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30810AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30810AP\"></sup>the kings of the earth and the great men and the commanders and the rich and the strong and every slave and free man hid themselves in the caves and among the rocks of the mountains;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and they *<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30811AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30811AQ\"></sup>said to the mountains and to the rocks, “Fall on us and hide us from the presence of Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30811AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30811AR\"></sup>who sits on the throne, and from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30811AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30811AS\"></sup>wrath of the Lamb;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30812AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30812AT\"></sup>the great day of their wrath has come, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30812AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30812AU\"></sup>who is able to stand?”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>After this I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30813A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30813A\"></sup>four angels standing at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30813B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30813B\"></sup>four corners of the earth, holding back <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30813C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30813C\"></sup>the four winds of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30813D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30813D\"></sup>so that no wind would blow on the earth or on the sea or on any tree.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw another angel ascending <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30814E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30814E\"></sup>from the rising of the sun, having the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30814F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30814F\"></sup>seal of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30814G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30814G\"></sup>the living God; and he cried out with a loud voice to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30814H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30814H\"></sup>four angels to whom it was granted to harm the earth and the sea,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30815I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30815I\"></sup>Do not harm the earth or the sea or the trees until we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30815J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30815J\"></sup>sealed the bond-servants of our God on their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30815K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30815K\"></sup>foreheads.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And I heard the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30816L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30816L\"></sup>number of those who were sealed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30816M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30816M\"></sup>one hundred and forty-four thousand sealed from every tribe of the sons of Israel:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>from the tribe of Judah, twelve thousand <i>were</i> sealed, from the tribe of Reuben twelve thousand, from the tribe of Gad twelve thousand,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>from the tribe of Asher twelve thousand, from the tribe of Naphtali twelve thousand, from the tribe of Manasseh twelve thousand,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>from the tribe of Simeon twelve thousand, from the tribe of Levi twelve thousand, from the tribe of Issachar twelve thousand,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>from the tribe of Zebulun twelve thousand, from the tribe of Joseph twelve thousand, from the tribe of Benjamin, twelve thousand <i>were</i> sealed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>After these things I looked, and behold, a great multitude which no one could count, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30821N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30821N\"></sup>every nation and <i>all</i> tribes and peoples and tongues, standing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30821O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30821O\"></sup>before the throne and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30821P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30821P\"></sup>before the Lamb, clothed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30821Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30821Q\"></sup>white robes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30821R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30821R\"></sup>palm branches <i>were</i> in their hands;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and they cry out with a loud voice, saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30822S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30822S\"></sup>Salvation to our God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30822T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30822T\"></sup>who sits on the throne, and to the Lamb.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And all the angels were standing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30823U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30823U\"></sup>around the throne and <i>around</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30823V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30823V\"></sup>the elders and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30823W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30823W\"></sup>four living creatures; and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30823X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30823X\"></sup>fell on their faces before the throne and worshiped God,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30824Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30824Y\"></sup>Amen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30824Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30824Z\"></sup>blessing and glory and wisdom and thanksgiving and honor and power and might, <i>be</i> to our God forever and ever. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30824AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30824AA\"></sup>Amen.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then one of the elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30825AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30825AB\"></sup>answered, saying to me, “These who are clothed in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30825AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30825AC\"></sup>white robes, who are they, and where have they come from?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I said to him, “My lord, you know.” And he said to me, “These are the ones who come out of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30826AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30826AD\"></sup>great tribulation, and they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30826AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30826AE\"></sup>washed their robes and made them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30826AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30826AF\"></sup>white in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30826AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30826AG\"></sup>blood of the Lamb.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For this reason, they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30827AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30827AH\"></sup>before the throne of God; and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30827AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30827AI\"></sup>serve Him day and night in His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30827AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30827AJ\"></sup>temple; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30827AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30827AK\"></sup>He who sits on the throne will spread His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30827AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30827AL\"></sup>tabernacle over them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30828AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30828AM\"></sup>They will hunger no longer, nor thirst anymore; nor will the sun beat down on them, nor any heat;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>for the Lamb in the center of the throne will be their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30829AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30829AN\"></sup>shepherd, and will guide them to springs of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30829AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30829AO\"></sup>water of life; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30829AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30829AP\"></sup>God will wipe every tear from their eyes.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>When the Lamb broke the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30830A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30830A\"></sup>seventh seal, there was silence in heaven for about half an hour.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30831B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30831B\"></sup>the seven angels who stand before God, and seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30831C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30831C\"></sup>trumpets were given to them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30832D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30832D\"></sup>Another angel came and stood at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30832E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30832E\"></sup>altar, holding a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30832F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30832F\"></sup>golden censer; and much <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30832G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30832G\"></sup>incense was given to him, so that he might add it to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30832H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30832H\"></sup>prayers of all the saints on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30832I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30832I\"></sup>golden altar which was before the throne.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30833J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30833J\"></sup>the smoke of the incense, with the prayers of the saints, went up before God out of the angel’s hand.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the angel took the censer and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30834K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30834K\"></sup>filled it with the fire of the altar, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30834L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30834L\"></sup>threw it to the earth; and there followed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30834M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30834M\"></sup>peals of thunder and sounds and flashes of lightning and an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30834N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30834N\"></sup>earthquake.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30835O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30835O\"></sup>And the seven angels who had the seven trumpets prepared themselves to sound them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The first sounded, and there came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30836P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30836P\"></sup>hail and fire, mixed with blood, and they were thrown to the earth; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30836Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30836Q\"></sup>a third of the earth was burned up, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30836R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30836R\"></sup>a third of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30836S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30836S\"></sup>trees were burned up, and all the green <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30836T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30836T\"></sup>grass was burned up.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The second angel sounded, and <i>something</i> like a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30837U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30837U\"></sup>mountain burning with fire was thrown into the sea; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30837V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30837V\"></sup>a third of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30837W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30837W\"></sup>sea became blood,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30838X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30838X\"></sup>a third of the creatures which were in the sea and had life, died; and a third of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30838Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30838Y\"></sup>ships were destroyed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The third angel sounded, and a great star <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30839Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30839Z\"></sup>fell from heaven, burning like a torch, and it fell on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30839AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30839AA\"></sup>third of the rivers and on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30839AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30839AB\"></sup>springs of waters.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The name of the star is called Wormwood; and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30840AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30840AC\"></sup>third of the waters became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30840AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30840AD\"></sup>wormwood, and many men died from the waters, because they were made bitter.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The fourth angel sounded, and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30841AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30841AE\"></sup>third of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30841AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30841AF\"></sup>sun and a third of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30841AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30841AG\"></sup>moon and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30841AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30841AH\"></sup>third of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30841AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30841AI\"></sup>stars were struck, so that a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30841AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30841AJ\"></sup>third of them would be darkened and the day would not shine for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30841AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30841AK\"></sup>third of it, and the night in the same way.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then I looked, and I heard an eagle flying in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30842AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30842AL\"></sup>midheaven, saying with a loud voice, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30842AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30842AM\"></sup>Woe, woe, woe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30842AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30842AN\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth, because of the remaining blasts of the trumpet of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30842AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30842AO\"></sup>three angels who are about to sound!”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30843A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30843A\"></sup>fifth angel sounded, and I saw a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30843B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30843B\"></sup>star from heaven which had fallen to the earth; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30843C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30843C\"></sup>key of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30843D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30843D\"></sup>bottomless pit was given to him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He opened the bottomless pit, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30844E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30844E\"></sup>smoke went up out of the pit, like the smoke of a great furnace; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30844F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30844F\"></sup>the sun and the air were darkened by the smoke of the pit.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then out of the smoke came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30845G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30845G\"></sup>locusts upon the earth, and power was given them, as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30845H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30845H\"></sup>scorpions of the earth have power.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They were told not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30846I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30846I\"></sup>hurt the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30846J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30846J\"></sup>grass of the earth, nor any green thing, nor any tree, but only the men who do not have the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30846K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30846K\"></sup>seal of God on their foreheads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And they were not permitted to kill anyone, but to torment for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30847L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30847L\"></sup>five months; and their torment was like the torment of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30847M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30847M\"></sup>scorpion when it stings a man.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And in those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30848N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30848N\"></sup>men will seek death and will not find it; they will long to die, and death flees from them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30849O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30849O\"></sup>appearance of the locusts was like horses prepared for battle; and on their heads appeared to be crowns like gold, and their faces were like the faces of men.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They had hair like the hair of women, and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30850P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30850P\"></sup>teeth were like <i>the teeth</i> of lions.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They had breastplates like breastplates of iron; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30851Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30851Q\"></sup>sound of their wings was like the sound of chariots, of many horses rushing to battle.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They have tails like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30852R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30852R\"></sup>scorpions, and stings; and in their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30852S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30852S\"></sup>tails is their power to hurt men for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30852T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30852T\"></sup>five months.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They have as king over them, the angel of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30853U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30853U\"></sup>abyss; his name in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30853V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30853V\"></sup>Hebrew is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30853W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30853W\"></sup>Abaddon, and in the Greek he has the name Apollyon.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30854X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30854X\"></sup>The first woe is past; behold, two woes are still coming after these things.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the sixth angel sounded, and I heard a voice from the four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30855Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30855Y\"></sup>horns of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30855Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30855Z\"></sup>golden altar which is before God,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>one saying to the sixth angel who had the trumpet, “Release the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30856AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30856AA\"></sup>four angels who are bound at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30856AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30856AB\"></sup>great river Euphrates.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the four angels, who had been prepared for the hour and day and month and year, were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30857AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30857AC\"></sup>released, so that they would kill a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30857AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30857AD\"></sup>third of mankind.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The number of the armies of the horsemen was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30858AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30858AE\"></sup>two hundred million; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30858AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30858AF\"></sup>I heard the number of them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And this is how I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30859AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30859AG\"></sup>in the vision the horses and those who sat on them: <i>the riders</i> had breastplates <i>the color</i> of fire and of hyacinth and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30859AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30859AH\"></sup>brimstone; and the heads of the horses are like the heads of lions; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30859AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30859AI\"></sup>out of their mouths proceed fire and smoke and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30859AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30859AJ\"></sup>brimstone.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30860AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30860AK\"></sup>third of mankind was killed by these three plagues, by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30860AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30860AL\"></sup>fire and the smoke and the brimstone which proceeded out of their mouths.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For the power of the horses is in their mouths and in their tails; for their tails are like serpents and have heads, and with them they do harm.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The rest of mankind, who were not killed by these plagues, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30862AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30862AM\"></sup>did not repent of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30862AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30862AN\"></sup>the works of their hands, so as not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30862AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30862AO\"></sup>worship demons, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30862AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30862AP\"></sup>the idols of gold and of silver and of brass and of stone and of wood, which can neither see nor hear nor walk;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30863AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30863AQ\"></sup>did not repent of their murders nor of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30863AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30863AR\"></sup>sorceries nor of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30863AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30863AS\"></sup>immorality nor of their thefts."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>I saw another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30864A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30864A\"></sup>strong angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30864B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30864B\"></sup>coming down out of heaven, clothed with a cloud; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30864C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30864C\"></sup>rainbow was upon his head, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30864D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30864D\"></sup>his face was like the sun, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30864E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30864E\"></sup>feet like pillars of fire;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and he had in his hand a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30865F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30865F\"></sup>little book which was open. He placed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30865G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30865G\"></sup>his right foot on the sea and his left on the land;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and he cried out with a loud voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30866H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30866H\"></sup>as when a lion roars; and when he had cried out, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30866I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30866I\"></sup>seven peals of thunder uttered their voices.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When the seven peals of thunder had spoken, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30867J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30867J\"></sup>I was about to write; and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30867K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30867K\"></sup>heard a voice from heaven saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30867L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30867L\"></sup>Seal up the things which the seven peals of thunder have spoken and do not write them.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the angel whom I saw standing on the sea and on the land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30868M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30868M\"></sup>lifted up his right hand to heaven,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30869N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30869N\"></sup>and swore by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30869O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30869O\"></sup>Him who lives forever and ever, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30869P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30869P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">who created heaven and the things in it, and the earth and the things in it, and the sea and the things in it</span>, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30869Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30869Q\"></sup>there will be delay no longer,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>but in the days of the voice of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30870R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30870R\"></sup>seventh angel, when he is about to sound, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30870S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30870S\"></sup>the mystery of God is finished, as He preached to His servants the prophets.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30871T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30871T\"></sup>the voice which I heard from heaven, <i>I heard</i> again speaking with me, and saying, “Go, take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30871U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30871U\"></sup>the book which is open in the hand of the angel who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30871V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30871V\"></sup>stands on the sea and on the land.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So I went to the angel, telling him to give me the little book. And he *said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30872W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30872W\"></sup>Take it and eat it; it will make your stomach bitter, but in your mouth it will be sweet as honey.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I took the little book out of the angel’s hand and ate it, and in my mouth it was sweet as honey; and when I had eaten it, my stomach was made bitter.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30874X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30874X\"></sup>they *said to me, “You must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30874Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30874Y\"></sup>prophesy again concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30874Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30874Z\"></sup>many peoples and nations and tongues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30874AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30874AA\"></sup>kings.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Then there was given me a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30875A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30875A\"></sup>measuring rod like a staff; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30875B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30875B\"></sup>someone said, “Get up and measure the temple of God and the altar, and those who worship in it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Leave out the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30876C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30876C\"></sup>court which is outside the temple and do not measure it, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30876D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30876D\"></sup>it has been given to the nations; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30876E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30876E\"></sup>tread under foot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30876F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30876F\"></sup>the holy city for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30876G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30876G\"></sup>forty-two months.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I will grant <i>authority</i> to my two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30877H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30877H\"></sup>witnesses, and they will prophesy for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30877I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30877I\"></sup>twelve hundred and sixty days, clothed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30877J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30877J\"></sup>sackcloth.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>These are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30878K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30878K\"></sup>two olive trees and the two lampstands that stand before the Lord of the earth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And if anyone wants to harm them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30879L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30879L\"></sup>fire flows out of their mouth and devours their enemies; so if anyone wants to harm them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30879M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30879M\"></sup>he must be killed in this way.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>These have the power to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30880N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30880N\"></sup>shut up the sky, so that rain will not fall during <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30880O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30880O\"></sup>the days of their prophesying; and they have power over the waters to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30880P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30880P\"></sup>turn them into blood, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30880Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30880Q\"></sup>to strike the earth with every plague, as often as they desire.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When they have finished their testimony, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30881R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30881R\"></sup>the beast that comes up out of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30881S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30881S\"></sup>abyss will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30881T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30881T\"></sup>make war with them, and overcome them and kill them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And their dead bodies <i>will lie</i> in the street of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30882U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30882U\"></sup>great city which mystically is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30882V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30882V\"></sup>Sodom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30882W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30882W\"></sup>Egypt, where also their Lord was crucified.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Those from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30883X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30883X\"></sup>the peoples and tribes and tongues and nations <i>will</i> look at their dead bodies for three and a half days, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30883Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30883Y\"></sup>will not permit their dead bodies to be laid in a tomb.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30884Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30884Z\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth <i>will</i> rejoice over them and celebrate; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30884AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30884AA\"></sup>send gifts to one another, because these two prophets tormented <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30884AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30884AB\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But after the three and a half days, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30885AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30885AC\"></sup>the breath of life from God came into them, and they stood on their feet; and great fear fell upon those who were watching them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And they heard a loud voice from heaven saying to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30886AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30886AD\"></sup>Come up here.” Then they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30886AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30886AE\"></sup>went up into heaven in the cloud, and their enemies watched them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And in that hour there was a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30887AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30887AF\"></sup>earthquake, and a tenth of the city fell; seven thousand people were killed in the earthquake, and the rest were terrified and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30887AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30887AG\"></sup>gave glory to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30887AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30887AH\"></sup>God of heaven.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The second <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30888AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30888AI\"></sup>woe is past; behold, the third woe is coming quickly.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30889AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30889AJ\"></sup>seventh angel sounded; and there were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30889AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30889AK\"></sup>loud voices in heaven, saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30889AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30889AL\"></sup>The kingdom of the world has become <i>the kingdom</i> of our Lord and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30889AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30889AM\"></sup>His Christ; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30889AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30889AN\"></sup>He will reign forever and ever.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the twenty-four elders, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30890AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30890AO\"></sup>sit on their thrones before God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30890AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30890AP\"></sup>fell on their faces and worshiped God,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>saying,“We give You thanks, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30891AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30891AQ\"></sup>O Lord God, the Almighty, who are and who were, because You have taken Your great power and have begun to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30891AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30891AR\"></sup>reign.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30892AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30892AS\"></sup>the nations were enraged, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30892AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30892AT\"></sup>Your wrath came, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30892AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30892AU\"></sup>the time <i>came</i> for the dead to be judged, and <i>the time</i> to reward Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30892AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30892AV\"></sup>bond-servants the prophets and the saints and those who fear Your name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30892AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30892AW\"></sup>the small and the great, and to destroy those who destroy the earth.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30893AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30893AX\"></sup>the temple of God which is in heaven was opened; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30893AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30893AY\"></sup>the ark of His covenant appeared in His temple, and there were flashes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30893AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30893AZ\"></sup>lightning and sounds and peals of thunder and an earthquake and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30893BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30893BA\"></sup>great hailstorm."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>A great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30894A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30894A\"></sup>sign appeared <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30894B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30894B\"></sup>in heaven: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30894C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30894C\"></sup>a woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30894D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30894D\"></sup>clothed with the sun, and the moon under her feet, and on her head a crown of twelve stars;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and she was with child; and she *<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30895E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30895E\"></sup>cried out, being in labor and in pain to give birth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30896F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30896F\"></sup>another sign appeared in heaven: and behold, a great red <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30896G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30896G\"></sup>dragon having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30896H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30896H\"></sup>seven heads and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30896I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30896I\"></sup>ten horns, and on his heads <i>were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30896J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30896J\"></sup>seven diadems.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And his tail *swept away a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30897K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30897K\"></sup>third of the stars of heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30897L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30897L\"></sup>threw them to the earth. And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30897M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30897M\"></sup>dragon stood before the woman who was about to give birth, so that when she gave birth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30897N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30897N\"></sup>he might devour her child.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30898O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30898O\"></sup>she gave birth to a son, a male <i>child</i>, who is to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30898P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30898P\"></sup>rule all the nations with a rod of iron; and her child was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30898Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30898Q\"></sup>caught up to God and to His throne.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the woman fled into the wilderness where she *had a place prepared by God, so that there she would be nourished for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30899R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30899R\"></sup>one thousand two hundred and sixty days.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And there was war in heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30900S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30900S\"></sup>Michael and his angels waging war with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30900T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30900T\"></sup>dragon. The dragon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30900U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30900U\"></sup>his angels waged war,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and they were not strong enough, and there was no longer a place found for them in heaven.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30902V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30902V\"></sup>dragon was thrown down, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30902W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30902W\"></sup>serpent of old who is called the devil and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30902X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30902X\"></sup>Satan, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30902Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30902Y\"></sup>deceives the whole world; he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30902Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30902Z\"></sup>thrown down to the earth, and his angels were thrown down with him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30903AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30903AA\"></sup>a loud voice in heaven, saying,“Now the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30903AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30903AB\"></sup>salvation, and the power, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30903AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30903AC\"></sup>kingdom of our God and the authority of His Christ have come, for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30903AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30903AD\"></sup>accuser of our brethren has been thrown down, he who accuses them before our God day and night.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30904AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30904AE\"></sup>overcame him because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30904AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30904AF\"></sup>the blood of the Lamb and because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30904AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30904AG\"></sup>the word of their testimony, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30904AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30904AH\"></sup>did not love their life even when faced with death.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For this reason, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30905AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30905AI\"></sup>rejoice, O heavens and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30905AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30905AJ\"></sup>you who dwell in them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30905AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30905AK\"></sup>Woe to the earth and the sea, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30905AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30905AL\"></sup>the devil has come down to you, having great wrath, knowing that he has <i>only</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30905AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30905AM\"></sup>a short time.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30906AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30906AN\"></sup>dragon saw that he was thrown down to the earth, he persecuted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30906AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30906AO\"></sup>the woman who gave birth to the male <i>child</i>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30907AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30907AP\"></sup>two wings of the great eagle were given to the woman, so that she could fly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30907AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30907AQ\"></sup>into the wilderness to her place, where she *was nourished for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30907AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30907AR\"></sup>a time and times and half a time, from the presence of the serpent.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30908AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30908AS\"></sup>serpent poured water like a river out of his mouth after the woman, so that he might cause her to be swept away with the flood.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But the earth helped the woman, and the earth opened its mouth and drank up the river which the dragon poured out of his mouth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So the dragon was enraged with the woman, and went off to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30910AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30910AT\"></sup>make war with the rest of her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30910AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30910AU\"></sup>children, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30910AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30910AV\"></sup>keep the commandments of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30910AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30910AW\"></sup>hold to the testimony of Jesus."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>And the dragon stood on the sand of the seashore.Then I saw a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30911A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30911A\"></sup>beast coming up out of the sea, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30911B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30911B\"></sup>ten horns and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30911C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30911C\"></sup>seven heads, and on his horns <i>were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30911D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30911D\"></sup>ten diadems, and on his heads <i>were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30911E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30911E\"></sup>blasphemous names.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the beast which I saw was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30912F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30912F\"></sup>like a leopard, and his feet were like <i>those</i> of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30912G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30912G\"></sup>a bear, and his mouth like the mouth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30912H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30912H\"></sup>a lion. And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30912I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30912I\"></sup>dragon gave him his power and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30912J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30912J\"></sup>throne and great authority.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><i>I saw</i> one of his heads as if it had been slain, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30913K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30913K\"></sup>fatal wound was healed. And the whole earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30913L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30913L\"></sup>was amazed <i>and followed</i> after the beast;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>they worshiped the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30914M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30914M\"></sup>dragon because he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30914N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30914N\"></sup>gave his authority to the beast; and they worshiped the beast, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30914O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30914O\"></sup>Who is like the beast, and who is able to wage war with him?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>There was given to him a mouth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30915P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30915P\"></sup>speaking arrogant words and blasphemies, and authority to act for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30915Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30915Q\"></sup>forty-two months was given to him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he opened his mouth in blasphemies against God, to blaspheme His name and His tabernacle, <i>that is</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30916R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30916R\"></sup>those who dwell in heaven.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It was also given to him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30917S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30917S\"></sup>make war with the saints and to overcome them, and authority over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30917T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30917T\"></sup>every tribe and people and tongue and nation was given to him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30918U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30918U\"></sup>dwell on the earth will worship him, <i>everyone</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30918V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30918V\"></sup>whose name has not been written <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30918W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30918W\"></sup>from the foundation of the world in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30918X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30918X\"></sup>book of life of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30918Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30918Y\"></sup>the Lamb who has been slain.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30919Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30919Z\"></sup>If anyone has an ear, let him hear.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30920AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30920AA\"></sup>If anyone <i>is destined</i> for captivity, to captivity he goes; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30920AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30920AB\"></sup>if anyone kills with the sword, with the sword he must be killed. Here is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30920AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30920AC\"></sup>the perseverance and the faith of the saints.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30921AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30921AD\"></sup>I saw another beast coming up out of the earth; and he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30921AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30921AE\"></sup>two horns like a lamb and he spoke as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30921AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30921AF\"></sup>dragon.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30922AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30922AG\"></sup>exercises all the authority of the first beast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30922AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30922AH\"></sup>in his presence. And he makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30922AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30922AI\"></sup>the earth and those who dwell in it to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30922AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30922AJ\"></sup>worship the first beast, whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30922AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30922AK\"></sup>fatal wound was healed.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30923AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30923AL\"></sup>performs great signs, so that he even makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30923AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30923AM\"></sup>fire come down out of heaven to the earth in the presence of men.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30924AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30924AN\"></sup>deceives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30924AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30924AO\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30924AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30924AP\"></sup>the signs which it was given him to perform <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30924AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30924AQ\"></sup>in the presence of the beast, telling those who dwell on the earth to make an image to the beast who *had the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30924AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30924AR\"></sup>wound of the sword and has come to life.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And it was given to him to give breath to the image of the beast, so that the image of the beast would even speak and cause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30925AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30925AS\"></sup>as many as do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30925AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30925AT\"></sup>worship the image of the beast to be killed.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he causes all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30926AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30926AU\"></sup>the small and the great, and the rich and the poor, and the free men and the slaves, to be given a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30926AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30926AV\"></sup>mark on their right hand or on their forehead,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and <i>he provides</i> that no one will be able to buy or to sell, except the one who has the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30927AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30927AW\"></sup>mark, <i>either</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30927AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30927AX\"></sup>the name of the beast or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30927AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30927AY\"></sup>the number of his name.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30928AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30928AZ\"></sup>Here is wisdom. Let him who has understanding calculate the number of the beast, for the number is that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30928BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30928BA\"></sup>of a man; and his number is six hundred and sixty-six."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Then I looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30929A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30929A\"></sup>the Lamb <i>was</i> standing on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30929B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30929B\"></sup>Mount Zion, and with Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30929C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30929C\"></sup>one hundred and forty-four thousand, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30929D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30929D\"></sup>His name and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30929E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30929E\"></sup>name of His Father written <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30929F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30929F\"></sup>on their foreheads.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I heard a voice from heaven, like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30930G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30930G\"></sup>the sound of many waters and like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30930H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30930H\"></sup>sound of loud thunder, and the voice which I heard <i>was</i> like <i>the sound</i> of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30930I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30930I\"></sup>harpists playing on their harps.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they *sang <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30931J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30931J\"></sup>a new song before the throne and before the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30931K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30931K\"></sup>four living creatures and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30931L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30931L\"></sup>elders; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30931M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30931M\"></sup>no one could learn the song except the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30931N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30931N\"></sup>one hundred and forty-four thousand who had been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30931O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30931O\"></sup>purchased from the earth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30932P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30932P\"></sup>These are the ones who have not been defiled with women, for they have kept themselves chaste. These <i>are</i> the ones who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30932Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30932Q\"></sup>follow the Lamb wherever He goes. These have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30932R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30932R\"></sup>purchased from among men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30932S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30932S\"></sup>as first fruits to God and to the Lamb.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30933T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30933T\"></sup>no lie was found in their mouth; they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30933U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30933U\"></sup>blameless.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I saw another angel flying in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30934V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30934V\"></sup>midheaven, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30934W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30934W\"></sup>an eternal gospel to preach to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30934X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30934X\"></sup>those who live on the earth, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30934Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30934Y\"></sup>every nation and tribe and tongue and people;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and he said with a loud voice, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30935Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30935Z\"></sup>Fear God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30935AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30935AA\"></sup>give Him glory, because the hour of His judgment has come; worship Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30935AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30935AB\"></sup>made the heaven and the earth and sea and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30935AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30935AC\"></sup>springs of waters.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And another angel, a second one, followed, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30936AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30936AD\"></sup>Fallen, fallen is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30936AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30936AE\"></sup>Babylon the great, she who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30936AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30936AF\"></sup>made all the nations drink of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30936AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30936AG\"></sup>wine of the passion of her immorality.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then another angel, a third one, followed them, saying with a loud voice, “If anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30937AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30937AH\"></sup>worships the beast and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30937AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30937AI\"></sup>image, and receives a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30937AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30937AJ\"></sup>mark on his forehead or on his hand,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>he also will drink of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30938AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30938AK\"></sup>wine of the wrath of God, which is mixed in full strength <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30938AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30938AL\"></sup>in the cup of His anger; and he will be tormented with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30938AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30938AM\"></sup>fire and brimstone in the presence of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30938AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30938AN\"></sup>holy angels and in the presence of the Lamb.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30939AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30939AO\"></sup>smoke of their torment goes up forever and ever; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30939AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30939AP\"></sup>they have no rest day and night, those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30939AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30939AQ\"></sup>worship the beast and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30939AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30939AR\"></sup>image, and whoever receives the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30939AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30939AS\"></sup>mark of his name.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Here is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30940AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30940AT\"></sup>the perseverance of the saints who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30940AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30940AU\"></sup>keep the commandments of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30940AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30940AV\"></sup>their faith in Jesus.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I heard a voice from heaven, saying, “Write, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30941AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30941AW\"></sup>Blessed are the dead who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30941AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30941AX\"></sup>die in the Lord from now on!’” “Yes,” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30941AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30941AY\"></sup>says the Spirit, “so that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30941AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30941AZ\"></sup>rest from their labors, for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30941BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30941BA\"></sup>deeds follow with them.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then I looked, and behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30942BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30942BB\"></sup>white cloud, and sitting on the cloud <i>was</i> one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30942BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30942BC\"></sup>like a son of man, having a golden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30942BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30942BD\"></sup>crown on His head and a sharp sickle in His hand.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And another angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30943BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30943BE\"></sup>came out of the temple, crying out with a loud voice to Him who sat on the cloud, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30943BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30943BF\"></sup>Put in your sickle and reap, for the hour to reap has come, because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30943BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30943BG\"></sup>harvest of the earth is ripe.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then He who sat on the cloud swung His sickle over the earth, and the earth was reaped.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And another angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30945BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30945BH\"></sup>came out of the temple which is in heaven, and he also had a sharp sickle.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then another angel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30946BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30946BI\"></sup>the one who has power over fire, came out from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30946BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30946BJ\"></sup>the altar; and he called with a loud voice to him who had the sharp sickle, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30946BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30946BK\"></sup>Put in your sharp sickle and gather the clusters from the vine of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30946BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30946BL\"></sup>because her grapes are ripe.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So the angel swung his sickle to the earth and gathered <i>the clusters from</i> the vine of the earth, and threw them into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30947BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30947BM\"></sup>the great wine press of the wrath of God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30948BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30948BN\"></sup>the wine press was trodden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30948BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30948BO\"></sup>outside the city, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30948BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30948BP\"></sup>blood came out from the wine press, up to the horses’ bridles, for a distance of two hundred miles."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30949A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30949A\"></sup>another sign in heaven, great and marvelous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30949B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30949B\"></sup>seven angels who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30949C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30949C\"></sup>seven plagues, <i>which are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30949D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30949D\"></sup>the last, because in them the wrath of God is finished.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw something like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30950E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30950E\"></sup>sea of glass mixed with fire, and those who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30950F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30950F\"></sup>been victorious over the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30950G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30950G\"></sup>beast and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30950H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30950H\"></sup>his image and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30950I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30950I\"></sup>number of his name, standing on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30950J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30950J\"></sup>sea of glass, holding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30950K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30950K\"></sup>harps of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they *sang the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30951L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30951L\"></sup>song of Moses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30951M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30951M\"></sup>the bond-servant of God, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30951N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30951N\"></sup>song of the Lamb, saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30951O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30951O\"></sup>Great and marvelous are Your works,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30951P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30951P\"></sup>O Lord God, the Almighty;Righteous and true are Your ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30951Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30951Q\"></sup>King of the nations!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30952R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30952R\"></sup>Who will not fear, O Lord, and glorify Your name?For You alone are holy;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30952S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30952S\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">all the nations will come and worship before You</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For Your</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30952T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30952T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">righteous acts have been revealed</span>.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>After these things I looked, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30953U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30953U\"></sup>the temple of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30953V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30953V\"></sup>tabernacle of testimony in heaven was opened,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30954W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30954W\"></sup>seven angels who had the seven plagues <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30954X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30954X\"></sup>came out of the temple, clothed in linen, clean <i>and</i> bright, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30954Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30954Y\"></sup>girded around their chests with golden sashes.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then one of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30955Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30955Z\"></sup>four living creatures gave to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30955AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30955AA\"></sup>seven angels seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30955AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30955AB\"></sup>golden bowls full of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30955AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30955AC\"></sup>wrath of God, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30955AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30955AD\"></sup>lives forever and ever.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the temple was filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30956AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30956AE\"></sup>smoke from the glory of God and from His power; and no one was able to enter the temple until the seven plagues of the seven angels were finished."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Then I heard a loud voice from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30957A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30957A\"></sup>the temple, saying to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30957B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30957B\"></sup>seven angels, “Go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30957C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30957C\"></sup>pour out on the earth the seven bowls of the wrath of God.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So the first <i>angel</i> went and poured out his bowl <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30958D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30958D\"></sup>on the earth; and it became a loathsome and malignant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30958E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30958E\"></sup>sore on the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30958F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30958F\"></sup>who had the mark of the beast and who worshiped his image.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The second <i>angel</i> poured out his bowl <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30959G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30959G\"></sup>into the sea, and it became blood like <i>that</i> of a dead man; and every living thing in the sea died.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the third <i>angel</i> poured out his bowl into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30960H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30960H\"></sup>rivers and the springs of waters; and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30960I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30960I\"></sup>became blood.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And I heard the angel of the waters saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30961J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30961J\"></sup>Righteous are You, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30961K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30961K\"></sup>who are and who were, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30961L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30961L\"></sup>Holy One, because You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30961M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30961M\"></sup>judged these things;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>for they poured out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30962N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30962N\"></sup>the blood of saints and prophets, and You have given them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30962O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30962O\"></sup>blood to drink. They deserve it.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30963P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30963P\"></sup>the altar saying, “Yes, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30963Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30963Q\"></sup>Lord God, the Almighty, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30963R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30963R\"></sup>true and righteous are Your judgments.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The fourth <i>angel</i> poured out his bowl upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30964S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30964S\"></sup>the sun, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30964T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30964T\"></sup>and it was given to it to scorch men with fire.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Men were scorched with fierce heat; and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30965U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30965U\"></sup>blasphemed the name of God who has the power over these plagues, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30965V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30965V\"></sup>did not repent so as to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30965W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30965W\"></sup>give Him glory.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the fifth <i>angel</i> poured out his bowl on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30966X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30966X\"></sup>throne of the beast, and his kingdom became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30966Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30966Y\"></sup>darkened; and they gnawed their tongues because of pain,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30967Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30967Z\"></sup>blasphemed the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30967AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30967AA\"></sup>God of heaven because of their pains and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30967AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30967AB\"></sup>sores; and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30967AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30967AC\"></sup>did not repent of their deeds.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The sixth <i>angel</i> poured out his bowl on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30968AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30968AD\"></sup>great river, the Euphrates; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30968AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30968AE\"></sup>its water was dried up, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30968AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30968AF\"></sup>the way would be prepared for the kings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30968AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30968AG\"></sup>from the east.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I saw <i>coming</i> out of the mouth of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30969AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30969AH\"></sup>dragon and out of the mouth of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30969AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30969AI\"></sup>beast and out of the mouth of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30969AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30969AJ\"></sup>false prophet, three <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30969AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30969AK\"></sup>unclean spirits like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30969AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30969AL\"></sup>frogs;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>for they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30970AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30970AM\"></sup>spirits of demons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30970AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30970AN\"></sup>performing signs, which go out to the kings of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30970AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30970AO\"></sup>whole world, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30970AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30970AP\"></sup>gather them together for the war of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30970AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30970AQ\"></sup>great day of God, the Almighty.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>(“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30971AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30971AR\"></sup>I am coming like a thief. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30971AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30971AS\"></sup>Blessed is the one who stays awake and keeps his clothes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30971AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30971AT\"></sup>so that he will not walk about naked and men will not see his shame.”)",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30972AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30972AU\"></sup>gathered them together to the place which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30972AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30972AV\"></sup>in Hebrew is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30972AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30972AW\"></sup>Har-Magedon.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then the seventh <i>angel</i> poured out his bowl upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30973AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30973AX\"></sup>the air, and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30973AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30973AY\"></sup>loud voice came out of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30973AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30973AZ\"></sup>temple from the throne, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30973BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30973BA\"></sup>It is done.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And there were flashes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30974BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30974BB\"></sup>lightning and sounds and peals of thunder; and there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30974BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30974BC\"></sup>a great earthquake, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30974BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30974BD\"></sup>such as there had not been since man came to be upon the earth, so great an earthquake <i>was it, and</i> so mighty.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30975BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30975BE\"></sup>The great city was split into three parts, and the cities of the nations fell. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30975BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30975BF\"></sup>Babylon the great was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30975BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30975BG\"></sup>remembered before God, to give her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30975BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30975BH\"></sup>the cup of the wine of His fierce wrath.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30976BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30976BI\"></sup>every island fled away, and the mountains were not found.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30977BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30977BJ\"></sup>huge hailstones, about one hundred pounds each, *came down from heaven upon men; and men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30977BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30977BK\"></sup>blasphemed God because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30977BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30977BL\"></sup>plague of the hail, because its plague *was extremely severe."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30978A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30978A\"></sup>Then one of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30978B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30978B\"></sup>seven angels who had the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30978C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30978C\"></sup>seven bowls came and spoke with me, saying, “Come here, I will show you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30978D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30978D\"></sup>the judgment of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30978E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30978E\"></sup>great harlot who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30978F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30978F\"></sup>sits on many waters,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>with whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30979G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30979G\"></sup>the kings of the earth committed <i>acts of</i> immorality, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30979H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30979H\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30979I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30979I\"></sup>made drunk with the wine of her immorality.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30980J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30980J\"></sup>he carried me away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30980K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30980K\"></sup>in the Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30980L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30980L\"></sup>into a wilderness; and I saw a woman sitting on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30980M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30980M\"></sup>scarlet beast, full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30980N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30980N\"></sup>blasphemous names, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30980O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30980O\"></sup>seven heads and ten horns.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30981P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30981P\"></sup>was clothed in purple and scarlet, and adorned with gold and precious stones and pearls, having in her hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30981Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30981Q\"></sup>a gold cup full of abominations and of the unclean things of her immorality,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and on her forehead a name <i>was</i> written, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30982R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30982R\"></sup>mystery, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30982S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30982S\"></sup>BABYLON THE GREAT, THE MOTHER OF HARLOTS AND OF <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30982T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30982T\"></sup>THE ABOMINATIONS OF THE EARTH.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I saw the woman drunk with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30983U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30983U\"></sup>the blood of the saints, and with the blood of the witnesses of Jesus. When I saw her, I wondered greatly.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And the angel said to me, “Why do you wonder? I will tell you the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30984V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30984V\"></sup>mystery of the woman and of the beast that carries her, which has the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30984W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30984W\"></sup>seven heads and the ten horns.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985X\"></sup>The beast that you saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985Y\"></sup>was, and is not, and is about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985Z\"></sup>come up out of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985AA\"></sup>abyss and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985AB\"></sup>go to destruction. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985AC\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985AD\"></sup>whose name has not been written in the book of life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985AE\"></sup>from the foundation of the world, will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30985AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30985AF\"></sup>wonder when they see the beast, that he was and is not and will come.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30986AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30986AG\"></sup>Here is the mind which has wisdom. The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30986AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30986AH\"></sup>seven heads are seven mountains on which the woman sits,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and they are seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30987AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30987AI\"></sup>kings; five have fallen, one is, the other has not yet come; and when he comes, he must remain a little while.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The beast which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30988AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30988AJ\"></sup>was and is not, is himself also an eighth and is <i>one</i> of the seven, and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30988AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30988AK\"></sup>goes to destruction.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30989AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30989AL\"></sup>ten horns which you saw are ten kings who have not yet received a kingdom, but they receive authority as kings with the beast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30989AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30989AM\"></sup>for one hour.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>These have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30990AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30990AN\"></sup>one purpose, and they give their power and authority to the beast.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>These will wage <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30991AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30991AO\"></sup>war against the Lamb, and the Lamb will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30991AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30991AP\"></sup>overcome them, because He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30991AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30991AQ\"></sup>Lord of lords and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30991AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30991AR\"></sup>King of kings, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30991AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30991AS\"></sup>those who are with Him <i>are the</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30991AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30991AT\"></sup>called and chosen and faithful.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And he *said to me, “The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30992AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30992AU\"></sup>waters which you saw where the harlot sits, are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30992AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30992AV\"></sup>peoples and multitudes and nations and tongues.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30993AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30993AW\"></sup>ten horns which you saw, and the beast, these will hate the harlot and will make her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30993AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30993AX\"></sup>desolate and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30993AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30993AY\"></sup>naked, and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30993AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30993AZ\"></sup>eat her flesh and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30993BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30993BA\"></sup>burn her up with fire.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30994BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30994BB\"></sup>God has put it in their hearts to execute His purpose by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30994BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30994BC\"></sup>having a common purpose, and by giving their kingdom to the beast, until the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30994BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30994BD\"></sup>words of God will be fulfilled.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The woman whom you saw is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30995BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30995BE\"></sup>the great city, which reigns over the kings of the earth.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>After these things I saw another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30996A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30996A\"></sup>angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30996B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30996B\"></sup>coming down from heaven, having great authority, and the earth was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30996C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30996C\"></sup>illumined with his glory.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he cried out with a mighty voice, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30997D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30997D\"></sup>Fallen, fallen is Babylon the great! She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30997E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30997E\"></sup>has become a dwelling place of demons and a prison of every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30997F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30997F\"></sup>unclean spirit, and a prison of every unclean and hateful bird.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For all the nations have drunk of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30998G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30998G\"></sup>wine of the passion of her immorality, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30998H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30998H\"></sup>the kings of the earth have committed <i>acts of</i> immorality with her, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30998I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30998I\"></sup>merchants of the earth have become rich by the wealth of her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30998J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30998J\"></sup>sensuality.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I heard another voice from heaven, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-30999K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-30999K\"></sup>Come out of her, my people, so that you will not participate in her sins and receive of her plagues;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for her sins have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31000L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31000L\"></sup>piled up as high as heaven, and God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31000M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31000M\"></sup>remembered her iniquities.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31001N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31001N\"></sup>Pay her back even as she has paid, and give back <i>to her</i> double according to her deeds; in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31001O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31001O\"></sup>cup which she has mixed, mix twice as much for her.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31002P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31002P\"></sup>To the degree that she glorified herself and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31002Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31002Q\"></sup>lived sensuously, to the same degree give her torment and mourning; for she says in her heart, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31002R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31002R\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">sit</span> <i>as</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">a queen and I am not a widow</span>, and will never see mourning.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31003S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31003S\"></sup>in one day her plagues will come, pestilence and mourning and famine, and she will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31003T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31003T\"></sup>burned up with fire; for the Lord God who judges her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31003U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31003U\"></sup>is strong.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31004V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31004V\"></sup>the kings of the earth, who committed <i>acts of</i> immorality and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31004W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31004W\"></sup>lived sensuously with her, will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31004X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31004X\"></sup>weep and lament over her when they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31004Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31004Y\"></sup>see the smoke of her burning,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31005Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31005Z\"></sup>standing at a distance because of the fear of her torment, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31005AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31005AA\"></sup>Woe, woe, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31005AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31005AB\"></sup>the great city, Babylon, the strong city! For in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31005AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31005AC\"></sup>one hour your judgment has come.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31006AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31006AD\"></sup>merchants of the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31006AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31006AE\"></sup>weep and mourn over her, because no one buys their cargoes any more—",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>cargoes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31007AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31007AF\"></sup>gold and silver and precious stones and pearls and fine linen and purple and silk and scarlet, and every <i>kind of</i> citron wood and every article of ivory and every article <i>made</i> from very costly wood and bronze and iron and marble,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and cinnamon and spice and incense and perfume and frankincense and wine and olive oil and fine flour and wheat and cattle and sheep, and <i>cargoes</i> of horses and chariots and slaves and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31008AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31008AG\"></sup>human lives.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The fruit you long for has gone from you, and all things that were luxurious and splendid have passed away from you and <i>men</i> will no longer find them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31010AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31010AH\"></sup>merchants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31010AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31010AI\"></sup>these things, who became rich from her, will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31010AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31010AJ\"></sup>stand at a distance because of the fear of her torment, weeping and mourning,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31011AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31011AK\"></sup>Woe, woe, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31011AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31011AL\"></sup>the great city, she who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31011AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31011AM\"></sup>was clothed in fine linen and purple and scarlet, and adorned with gold and precious stones and pearls;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>for in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31012AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31012AN\"></sup>one hour such great wealth has been laid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31012AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31012AO\"></sup>waste!’ And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31012AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31012AP\"></sup>every shipmaster and every passenger and sailor, and as many as make their living by the sea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31012AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31012AQ\"></sup>stood at a distance,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31013AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31013AR\"></sup>crying out as they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31013AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31013AS\"></sup>saw the smoke of her burning, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31013AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31013AT\"></sup>What <i>city</i> is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31013AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31013AU\"></sup>the great city?’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And they threw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31014AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31014AV\"></sup>dust on their heads and were crying out, weeping and mourning, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31014AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31014AW\"></sup>Woe, woe, the great city, in which all who had ships at sea <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31014AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31014AX\"></sup>became rich by her wealth, for in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31014AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31014AY\"></sup>one hour she has been laid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31014AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31014AZ\"></sup>waste!’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31015BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31015BA\"></sup>Rejoice over her, O heaven, and you saints and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31015BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31015BB\"></sup>apostles and prophets, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31015BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31015BC\"></sup>God has pronounced judgment for you against her.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31016BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31016BD\"></sup>strong angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31016BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31016BE\"></sup>took up a stone like a great millstone and threw it into the sea, saying, “So will Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31016BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31016BF\"></sup>the great city, be thrown down with violence, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31016BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31016BG\"></sup>will not be found any longer.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31017BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31017BH\"></sup>the sound of harpists and musicians and flute-players and trumpeters will not be heard in you any longer; and no craftsman of any craft will be found in you any longer; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31017BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31017BI\"></sup>sound of a mill will not be heard in you any longer;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and the light of a lamp will not shine in you any longer; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31018BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31018BJ\"></sup>voice of the bridegroom and bride will not be heard in you any longer; for your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31018BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31018BK\"></sup>merchants were the great men of the earth, because all the nations were deceived <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31018BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31018BL\"></sup>by your sorcery.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And in her was found the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31019BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31019BM\"></sup>blood of prophets and of saints and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31019BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31019BN\"></sup>all who have been slain on the earth.”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>After these things I heard something like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31020A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31020A\"></sup>loud voice of a great multitude in heaven, saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31020B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31020B\"></sup>Hallelujah! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31020C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31020C\"></sup>Salvation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31020D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31020D\"></sup>glory and power belong to our God;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31021E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31021E\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">because His</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31021F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31021F\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">judgments are</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31021G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31021G\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">true and righteous</span>; for He has judged the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31021H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31021H\"></sup>great harlot who was corrupting the earth with her immorality, and <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He has</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31021I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31021I\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">avenged the blood of His bond-servants</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">on her</span>.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And a second time they said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31022J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31022J\"></sup>Hallelujah! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31022K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31022K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Her smoke rises up forever and ever</span>.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31023L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31023L\"></sup>twenty-four elders and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31023M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31023M\"></sup>four living creatures <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31023N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31023N\"></sup>fell down and worshiped God who sits on the throne saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31023O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31023O\"></sup>Amen. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31023P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31023P\"></sup>Hallelujah!”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And a voice came from the throne, saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31024Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31024Q\"></sup>Give praise to our God, all you His bond-servants, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31024R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31024R\"></sup>you who fear Him, the small and the great.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I heard <i>something</i> like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31025S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31025S\"></sup>the voice of a great multitude and like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31025T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31025T\"></sup>the sound of many waters and like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31025U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31025U\"></sup>sound of mighty peals of thunder, saying,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31025V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31025V\"></sup>Hallelujah! For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31025W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31025W\"></sup>Lord our God, the Almighty, reigns.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Let us rejoice and be glad and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31026X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31026X\"></sup>give the glory to Him, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31026Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31026Y\"></sup>the marriage of the Lamb has come and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31026Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31026Z\"></sup>bride has made herself ready.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It was given to her to clothe herself in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31027AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31027AA\"></sup>fine linen, bright <i>and</i> clean; for the fine linen is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31027AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31027AB\"></sup>righteous acts of the saints.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31028AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31028AC\"></sup>he *said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31028AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31028AD\"></sup>Write, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31028AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31028AE\"></sup>Blessed are those who are invited to the marriage supper of the Lamb.’” And he *said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31028AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31028AF\"></sup>These are true words of God.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31029AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31029AG\"></sup>I fell at his feet to worship him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31029AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31029AH\"></sup>But he *said to me, “Do not do that; I am a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31029AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31029AI\"></sup>fellow servant of yours and your brethren who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31029AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31029AJ\"></sup>hold the testimony of Jesus; worship God. For the testimony of Jesus is the spirit of prophecy.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31030AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31030AK\"></sup>heaven opened, and behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31030AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31030AL\"></sup>white horse, and He who sat on it <i>is</i> called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31030AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31030AM\"></sup>Faithful and True, and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31030AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31030AN\"></sup>righteousness He judges and wages war.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31031AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31031AO\"></sup>eyes <i>are</i> a flame of fire, and on His head <i>are</i> many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31031AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31031AP\"></sup>diadems; and He has a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31031AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31031AQ\"></sup>name written <i>on Him</i> which no one knows except Himself.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><i>He is</i> clothed with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31032AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31032AR\"></sup>robe dipped in blood, and His name is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31032AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31032AS\"></sup>The Word of God.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the armies which are in heaven, clothed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31033AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31033AT\"></sup>fine linen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31033AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31033AU\"></sup>white <i>and</i> clean, were following Him on white horses.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31034AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31034AV\"></sup>From His mouth comes a sharp sword, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31034AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31034AW\"></sup>with it He may strike down the nations, and He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31034AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31034AX\"></sup>rule them with a rod of iron; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31034AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31034AY\"></sup>He treads the wine press of the fierce wrath of God, the Almighty.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And on His robe and on His thigh He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31035AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31035AZ\"></sup>a name written, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31035BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31035BA\"></sup>KING OF KINGS, AND LORD OF LORDS.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then I saw an angel standing in the sun, and he cried out with a loud voice, saying to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31036BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31036BB\"></sup>all the birds which fly in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31036BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31036BC\"></sup>midheaven, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31036BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31036BD\"></sup>Come, assemble for the great supper of God,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>so that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31037BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31037BE\"></sup>eat the flesh of kings and the flesh of commanders and the flesh of mighty men and the flesh of horses and of those who sit on them and the flesh of all men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31037BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31037BF\"></sup>both free men and slaves, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31037BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31037BG\"></sup>small and great.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31038BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31038BH\"></sup>the beast and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31038BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31038BI\"></sup>the kings of the earth and their armies assembled to make war against Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31038BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31038BJ\"></sup>sat on the horse and against His army.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And the beast was seized, and with him the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31039BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31039BK\"></sup>false prophet who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31039BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31039BL\"></sup>performed the signs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31039BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31039BM\"></sup>in his presence, by which he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31039BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31039BN\"></sup>deceived those who had received the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31039BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31039BO\"></sup>mark of the beast and those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31039BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31039BP\"></sup>worshiped his image; these two were thrown alive into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31039BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31039BQ\"></sup>lake of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31039BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31039BR\"></sup>fire which burns with brimstone.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And the rest were killed with the sword which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31040BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31040BS\"></sup>came from the mouth of Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31040BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31040BT\"></sup>sat on the horse, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31040BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31040BU\"></sup>all the birds were filled with their flesh."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>Then I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31041A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31041A\"></sup>an angel coming down from heaven, holding the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31041B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31041B\"></sup>key of the abyss and a great chain in his hand.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he laid hold of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31042C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31042C\"></sup>dragon, the serpent of old, who is the devil and Satan, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31042D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31042D\"></sup>bound him for a thousand years;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and he threw him into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31043E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31043E\"></sup>abyss, and shut <i>it</i> and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31043F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31043F\"></sup>sealed <i>it</i> over him, so that he would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31043G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31043G\"></sup>not deceive the nations any longer, until the thousand years were completed; after these things he must be released for a short time.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044H\"></sup>thrones, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044I\"></sup>they sat on them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044J\"></sup>judgment was given to them. And I <i>saw</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044K\"></sup>the souls of those who had been beheaded because of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044L\"></sup>testimony of Jesus and because of the word of God, and those who had not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044M\"></sup>worshiped the beast or his image, and had not received the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044N\"></sup>mark on their forehead and on their hand; and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044O\"></sup>came to life and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31044P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31044P\"></sup>reigned with Christ for a thousand years.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The rest of the dead did not come to life until the thousand years were completed. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31045Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31045Q\"></sup>This is the first resurrection.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31046R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31046R\"></sup>Blessed and holy is the one who has a part in the first resurrection; over these the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31046S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31046S\"></sup>second death has no power, but they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31046T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31046T\"></sup>priests of God and of Christ and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31046U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31046U\"></sup>reign with Him for a thousand years.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the thousand years are completed, Satan will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31047V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31047V\"></sup>released from his prison,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and will come out to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31048W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31048W\"></sup>deceive the nations which are in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31048X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31048X\"></sup>four corners of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31048Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31048Y\"></sup>Gog and Magog, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31048Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31048Z\"></sup>gather them together for the war; the number of them is like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31048AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31048AA\"></sup>sand of the seashore.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31049AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31049AB\"></sup>came up on the broad plain of the earth and surrounded the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31049AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31049AC\"></sup>camp of the saints and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31049AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31049AD\"></sup>beloved city, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31049AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31049AE\"></sup>fire came down from heaven and devoured them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31050AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31050AF\"></sup>the devil who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31050AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31050AG\"></sup>deceived them was thrown into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31050AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31050AH\"></sup>lake of fire and brimstone, where the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31050AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31050AI\"></sup>beast and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31050AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31050AJ\"></sup>false prophet are also; and they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31050AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31050AK\"></sup>tormented day and night forever and ever.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I saw a great white <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31051AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31051AL\"></sup>throne and Him who sat upon it, from whose presence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31051AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31051AM\"></sup>earth and heaven fled away, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31051AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31051AN\"></sup>no place was found for them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And I saw the dead, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31052AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31052AO\"></sup>great and the small, standing before the throne, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31052AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31052AP\"></sup>books were opened; and another book was opened, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31052AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31052AQ\"></sup><i>the book</i> of life; and the dead <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31052AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31052AR\"></sup>were judged from the things which were written in the books, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31052AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31052AS\"></sup>according to their deeds.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the sea gave up the dead which were in it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31053AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31053AT\"></sup>death and Hades <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31053AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31053AU\"></sup>gave up the dead which were in them; and they were judged, every one <i>of them</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31053AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31053AV\"></sup>according to their deeds.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31054AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31054AW\"></sup>death and Hades were thrown into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31054AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31054AX\"></sup>the lake of fire. This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31054AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31054AY\"></sup>second death, the lake of fire.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And if anyone’s name was not found written in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31055AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31055AZ\"></sup>the book of life, he was thrown into the lake of fire."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>Then I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31056A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31056A\"></sup>a new heaven and a new earth; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31056B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31056B\"></sup>the first heaven and the first earth passed away, and there is no longer <i>any</i> sea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31057C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31057C\"></sup>the holy city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31057D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31057D\"></sup>new Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31057E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31057E\"></sup>coming down out of heaven from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31057F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31057F\"></sup>made ready as a bride adorned for her husband.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I heard a loud voice from the throne, saying, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31058G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31058G\"></sup>the tabernacle of God is among men, and He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31058H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31058H\"></sup>dwell among them, and they shall be His people, and God Himself will be among them,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31059I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31059I\"></sup>wipe away every tear from their eyes; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31059J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31059J\"></sup>there will no longer be <i>any</i> death; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31059K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31059K\"></sup>there will no longer be <i>any</i> mourning, or crying, or pain; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31059L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31059L\"></sup>the first things have passed away.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31060M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31060M\"></sup>He who sits on the throne said, “Behold, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31060N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31060N\"></sup>making all things new.” And He *said, “Write, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31060O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31060O\"></sup>these words are faithful and true.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then He said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31061P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31061P\"></sup>It is done. I am the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31061Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31061Q\"></sup>Alpha and the Omega, the beginning and the end. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31061R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31061R\"></sup>I will give to the one who thirsts from the spring of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31061S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31061S\"></sup>water of life without cost.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31062T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31062T\"></sup>He who overcomes will inherit these things, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31062U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31062U\"></sup>I will be his God and he will be My son.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31063V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31063V\"></sup>But for the cowardly and unbelieving and abominable and murderers and immoral persons and sorcerers and idolaters and all liars, their part <i>will be</i> in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31063W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31063W\"></sup>the lake that burns with fire and brimstone, which is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31063X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31063X\"></sup>second death.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31064Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31064Y\"></sup>Then one of the seven angels who had the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31064Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31064Z\"></sup>seven bowls full of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31064AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31064AA\"></sup>seven last plagues came and spoke with me, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31064AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31064AB\"></sup>Come here, I will show you the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31064AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31064AC\"></sup>bride, the wife of the Lamb.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31065AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31065AD\"></sup>he carried me away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31065AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31065AE\"></sup>in the Spirit to a great and high mountain, and showed me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31065AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31065AF\"></sup>the holy city, Jerusalem, coming down out of heaven from God,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31066AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31066AG\"></sup>the glory of God. Her brilliance was like a very costly stone, as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31066AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31066AH\"></sup>stone of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31066AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31066AI\"></sup>crystal-clear jasper.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It had a great and high wall, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31067AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31067AJ\"></sup>with twelve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31067AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31067AK\"></sup>gates, and at the gates twelve angels; and names <i>were</i> written on them, which are <i>the names</i> of the twelve tribes of the sons of Israel.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><i>There were</i> three gates on the east and three gates on the north and three gates on the south and three gates on the west.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the wall of the city had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31069AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31069AL\"></sup>twelve foundation stones, and on them <i>were</i> the twelve names of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31069AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31069AM\"></sup>twelve apostles of the Lamb.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The one who spoke with me had a gold measuring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31070AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31070AN\"></sup>rod to measure the city, and its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31070AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31070AO\"></sup>gates and its wall.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The city is laid out as a square, and its length is as great as the width; and he measured the city with the rod, fifteen hundred miles; its length and width and height are equal.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And he measured its wall, seventy-two yards, <i>according to</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31072AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31072AP\"></sup>human measurements, which are <i>also</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31072AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31072AQ\"></sup>angelic <i>measurements</i>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The material of the wall was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31073AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31073AR\"></sup>jasper; and the city was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31073AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31073AS\"></sup>pure gold, like clear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31073AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31073AT\"></sup>glass.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31074AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31074AU\"></sup>The foundation stones of the city wall were adorned with every kind of precious stone. The first foundation stone was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31074AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31074AV\"></sup>jasper; the second, sapphire; the third, chalcedony; the fourth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31074AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31074AW\"></sup>emerald;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>the fifth, sardonyx; the sixth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31075AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31075AX\"></sup>sardius; the seventh, chrysolite; the eighth, beryl; the ninth, topaz; the tenth, chrysoprase; the eleventh, jacinth; the twelfth, amethyst.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And the twelve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31076AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31076AY\"></sup>gates were twelve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31076AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31076AZ\"></sup>pearls; each one of the gates was a single pearl. And the street of the city was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31076BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31076BA\"></sup>pure gold, like transparent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31076BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31076BB\"></sup>glass.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31077BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31077BC\"></sup>no temple in it, for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31077BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31077BD\"></sup>Lord God the Almighty and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31077BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31077BE\"></sup>Lamb are its temple.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And the city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31078BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31078BF\"></sup>has no need of the sun or of the moon to shine on it, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31078BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31078BG\"></sup>the glory of God has illumined it, and its lamp <i>is</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31078BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31078BH\"></sup>Lamb.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31079BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31079BI\"></sup>The nations will walk by its light, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31079BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31079BJ\"></sup>kings of the earth will bring their glory into it.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In the daytime (for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31080BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31080BK\"></sup>there will be no night there) <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31080BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31080BL\"></sup>its gates <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31080BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31080BM\"></sup>will never be closed;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31081BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31081BN\"></sup>they will bring the glory and the honor of the nations into it;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31082BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31082BO\"></sup>nothing unclean, and no one who practices abomination and lying, shall ever come into it, but only those whose names are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31082BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31082BP\"></sup>written in the Lamb’s book of life."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31083A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31083A\"></sup>he showed me a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31083B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31083B\"></sup>river of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31083C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31083C\"></sup>water of life, clear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31083D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31083D\"></sup>as crystal, coming from the throne of God and of the Lamb,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>in the middle of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31084E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31084E\"></sup>its street. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31084F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31084F\"></sup>On either side of the river was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31084G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31084G\"></sup>the tree of life, bearing twelve <i>kinds of</i> fruit, yielding its fruit every month; and the leaves of the tree were for the healing of the nations.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31085H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31085H\"></sup>There will no longer be any curse; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31085I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31085I\"></sup>the throne of God and of the Lamb will be in it, and His bond-servants will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31085J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31085J\"></sup>serve Him;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31086K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31086K\"></sup>see His face, and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31086L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31086L\"></sup>name <i>will be</i> on their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31086M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31086M\"></sup>foreheads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31087N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31087N\"></sup>there will no longer be <i>any</i> night; and they will not have need <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31087O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31087O\"></sup>of the light of a lamp nor the light of the sun, because the Lord God will illumine them; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31087P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31087P\"></sup>reign forever and ever.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31088Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31088Q\"></sup>he said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31088R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31088R\"></sup>These words are faithful and true”; and the Lord, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31088S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31088S\"></sup>God of the spirits of the prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31088T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31088T\"></sup>sent His angel to show to His bond-servants the things which must soon take place.",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31089U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31089U\"></sup>I am coming quickly. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31089V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31089V\"></sup>Blessed is he who heeds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31089W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31089W\"></sup>the words of the prophecy of this book.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31090X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31090X\"></sup>I, John, am the one who heard and saw these things. And when I heard and saw, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31090Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31090Y\"></sup>I fell down to worship at the feet of the angel who showed me these things.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31091Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31091Z\"></sup>he *said to me, “Do not do that. I am a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31091AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31091AA\"></sup>fellow servant of yours and of your brethren the prophets and of those who heed the words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31091AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31091AB\"></sup>this book. Worship God.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And he *said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31092AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31092AC\"></sup>Do not seal up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31092AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31092AD\"></sup>the words of the prophecy of this book, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31092AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31092AE\"></sup>for the time is near.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31093AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31093AF\"></sup>Let the one who does wrong, still do wrong; and the one who is filthy, still be filthy; and let the one who is righteous, still practice righteousness; and the one who is holy, still keep himself holy.”",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31094AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31094AG\"></sup>I am coming quickly, and My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31094AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31094AH\"></sup>reward <i>is</i> with Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31094AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31094AI\"></sup>to render to every man according to what he has done.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I am the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31095AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31095AJ\"></sup>Alpha and the Omega, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31095AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31095AK\"></sup>the first and the last, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31095AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31095AL\"></sup>the beginning and the end.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Blessed are those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31096AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31096AM\"></sup>wash their robes, so that they may have the right to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31096AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31096AN\"></sup>the tree of life, and may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31096AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31096AO\"></sup>enter by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31096AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31096AP\"></sup>gates into the city.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31097AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31097AQ\"></sup>Outside are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31097AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31097AR\"></sup>dogs and the sorcerers and the immoral persons and the murderers and the idolaters, and everyone who loves and practices lying.",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31098AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31098AS\"></sup>I, Jesus, have sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31098AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31098AT\"></sup>My angel to testify to you these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31098AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31098AU\"></sup>for the churches. I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31098AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31098AV\"></sup>the root and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31098AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31098AW\"></sup>descendant of David, the bright <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31098AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31098AX\"></sup>morning star.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31099AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31099AY\"></sup>Spirit and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31099AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31099AZ\"></sup>bride say, “Come.” And let the one who hears say, “Come.” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31099BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31099BA\"></sup>let the one who is thirsty come; let the one who wishes take the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31099BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31099BB\"></sup>water of life without cost.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I testify to everyone who hears <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31100BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31100BC\"></sup>the words of the prophecy of this book: if anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31100BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31100BD\"></sup>adds to them, God will add to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31100BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31100BE\"></sup>the plagues which are written in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31100BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31100BF\"></sup>this book;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and if anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31101BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31101BG\"></sup>takes away from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31101BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31101BH\"></sup>words of the book of this prophecy, God will take away his part from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31101BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31101BI\"></sup>the tree of life and from the holy city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31101BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31101BJ\"></sup>which are written in this book.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31102BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31102BK\"></sup>testifies to these things says, <span class=\"woj\">“Yes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31102BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31102BL\"></sup>I am coming quickly.”</span> Amen. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31102BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31102BM\"></sup>Come, Lord Jesus.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-31103BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-31103BN\"></sup>The grace of the Lord Jesus be with all. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;